{"tid":1019630,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"tg紅線緣份計劃","createTime":"2019-02-13T05:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T07:37:45.000Z","uid":67905,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c377e7bbfea0ab35c4702b62489203fb9b1f712e","tid":1019630,"uid":67905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:26:30.000Z","msg":"講低你既資料 同你要求既對象條件等等 我再幫你地配對 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n配對準則：我會從年紀 興趣 大家既要求互相符合 等等各方面<br />\n所以希望大家打詳細啲唔好浪費大家時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZLK1m2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZLK1m2.jpg&h=8dfb5590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以請大家認真少少打多啲no pain no gain</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iM5yUGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiM5yUGE.jpg&h=00c2f74d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<strong><em>eg.<br />\n自己： <br />\n姓别<br />\n年紀<br />\n稱呼xxx<br />\n身高xxx cm<br />\n體重<br />\n興趣<br />\n學歷/工作<br />\n<br />\n對象條件：</em></strong><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n開既原因係<br />\n琴日睇左YouTube個紅線計劃live 睇完有興趣做類近既野。<br />\n<br />\n其次覺得有啲交友group麻麻地 所以自己想嘗試下，<br />\n<br />\n點解覺得麻麻地？<br />\n1：例如tg group 好多時新入到去有種傾唔埋既感覺<br />\n2：ig果啲交友 又唔知點解要send相比條友評分<br />\n3：如果係留tg po到 留tg 又會可能有多個既pm 搞到有啲人無覆or好快轉id。 <br />\n<br />\n大致上係咁多，po我相既 其實我放得tg出黎 就預咗比人睇我icon 我都唔明你咁樣係咪想人讚你叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我預左有負皮果啲 因爲之前都睇過有啲group話啲人厹果啲(紫xxx？？)<br />\n<br />\n最後係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家喜歡，歡迎比意見我改善更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a31cf01dece3cfb3636e0410e7d50dcb30be4c2","tid":1019630,"uid":67905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13